<p><b>perpetrators are held accountable (Austria); 
</b></p>
<p>125.49 <b>Continue to give priority to efforts aimed at the recognition and 
</b></p>
<p><b>protection of journalists and human rights defenders (Colombia); 
</b></p>
<p>125.50 <b>Respect and protect the right to freedom of expression and 
</b></p>
