</b></p>
<p><b>its operation, including its consistency with international human rights 
</b></p>
<p><b>standards, after a period of initial implementation (Ireland); 
</b></p>
<p>125.52 <b>Ensure effective implementation of the law on the protection of 
</b></p>
<p><b>human rights defenders, journalists, social communicators and justice officials 
